short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Modify YouTube thumbnails to include Your favorite mate, My Mate Nate!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Do you find yourselves having a boring experience searching videos on YouTube to find anything to watch? Or don't have enough for one of a kind thumbnail from your favorite Youtuber? Well, say goodbye to those problems with YouTube My Mate Nate-ify 24 hours!

"สวัสดีขร้าบผมมายเมทเนทและวันนี้เราจะมาอยู่บนปกคลิปบนYouTubeของคุณเป็นเวลา24ชั่วโมงนะขร้าบ"

This extension was inspired by MrBeastify by MagicJinn, including the source code of this extension. Thank you truly. https://github.com/MagicJinn/MrBeastify-Youtube

*Disclaimer, this is only a joke extension inspired by MrBeastify*

Fix 1.3: some images are not supposed to flip.
